# <a name="get-intrinsic-supversion-badgenpm-version-svgpackage-urlsup"></a>get-intrinsic <sup>[![Version Badge][npm-version-svg]][package-url]</sup>

[![dependency status][deps-svg]][deps-url]
[![dev dependency status][dev-deps-svg]][dev-deps-url]
[![License][license-image]][license-url]
[![Downloads][downloads-image]][downloads-url]

[![npm badge][npm-badge-png]][package-url]

처음에 필요한 시간에 모든 JS 언어 수준 내장 함수를 가져와서 강력하게 캐시합니다.

[JS 사양](https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-well-known-intrinsic-objects)에 설명된 구문을 참조하세요.

## <a name="example"></a>예

```js
var GetIntrinsic = require('get-intrinsic');
var assert = require('assert');

// static methods
assert.equal(GetIntrinsic('%Math.pow%'), Math.pow);
assert.equal(Math.pow(2, 3), 8);
assert.equal(GetIntrinsic('%Math.pow%')(2, 3), 8);
delete Math.pow;
assert.equal(GetIntrinsic('%Math.pow%')(2, 3), 8);

// instance methods
var arr = [1];
assert.equal(GetIntrinsic('%Array.prototype.push%'), Array.prototype.push);
assert.deepEqual(arr, [1]);

arr.push(2);
assert.deepEqual(arr, [1, 2]);

GetIntrinsic('%Array.prototype.push%').call(arr, 3);
assert.deepEqual(arr, [1, 2, 3]);

delete Array.prototype.push;
GetIntrinsic('%Array.prototype.push%').call(arr, 4);
assert.deepEqual(arr, [1, 2, 3, 4]);

// missing features
delete JSON.parse; // to simulate a real intrinsic that is missing in the environment
assert.throws(() => GetIntrinsic('%JSON.parse%'));
assert.equal(undefined, GetIntrinsic('%JSON.parse%', true));
```

## <a name="tests"></a>테스트
`npm install` 리포지토리를 복제하고 `npm test`을(를) 실행하기만 합니다.

[@ljharb](https://github.com/ljharb)으로 메일을 보내거나 보고할 잠재적인 보안 취약성이 있는지 경우 https://tidelift.com/security 를 참조하세요.
